A simple word and character counter in html and jQuery.
Capabilities include:
* Copy and Paste to textarea to show the count
* Update the count on every keystroke

Demo : http://deepumohan.com/projects/word-count/

jsFiddle: http://jsfiddle.net/deepumohanp/jZeKu/


Join the chat at https://gitter.im/word-count/Lobby
